### Trust Score API Tests
# Make sure your Next.js local server is running (e.g., on port 3000)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Calculate Initial Trust Score
# This is an unauthenticated endpoint for testing calculation logic.
# Returns { score, tier } based on the provided factors.

POST {{baseUrl}}/trust-score/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hasUploadedId": true,
  "hasUploadedSelfie": true,
  "phoneAgeMonths": 24,
  "hasLinkedBank": false,
  "hasIncomeDoc": true
}

###

